Data Structures
Here are the data structures with brief descriptions:
 CUart_ChanParamsUart channel config parameters IMP: Uart Channel Params passed to Uart_open function
 CUart_CrossBarEvtParamStructure to get the user param to enable the cross bar interrupt on M3 core
 CUart_FifoStatsUart FIFO Status
 CUart_FlowControlUart Flow Control Configuration
 CUart_ParamsUart Instance configuration parameters A pointer to such a structure is used when driver is instantiated
 CUart_StatsUart Statistics Collection Object IMP: Statistics are collected on a per-device basis for Uart
 CUart_TrigLvlUart TrigLvl Configuration
